        <item>
            <title>华为：Mate 70 每一颗晶片都有国产能力，网民指部份晶片仍由台积电代工</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/06/huawai-mate-70-all-chips-made-in-china/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawai-mate-70-all-chips-made-in-china</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/06/huawai-mate-70-all-chips-made-in-china/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 07:40:49 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate 70]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate 70 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kirin 9010]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kirin 9020]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1278921</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>日前华为（Huawei）发布采用「纯血鸿蒙」作业系统的 Mate 70 系列智能手机（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/27/huawei-mate-70-series/mobile-phone/">相关报道</a>）。昨日（ 5 日）正式开售，华为终端 BG 行政总裁何刚接受采访时表示：「华为 Mate 70 系列每一颗晶片都有（中）国产的能力。」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279592" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4ee8bc4d62c44d239046-694x430.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="430" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4ee8bc4d62c44d239046-694x430.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/4ee8bc4d62c44d239046.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲华为 BG 终端 CEO 何刚（左），图片来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1017/1017804.htm">快科技</a></p><p><br />根据报道，何刚表示华为所有晶片都具有中国生产能力量。曾任记者，现任紫牛基金合伙人张泉灵采访何刚时指，大家需要承认要由半导体角度出发的话，华为晶片与世界最高水平的工艺仍然有一段差距，不过华为已经在软硬件方面着手提升用户体验，因此她认为一般消费者用户不会感觉到有差距。张泉灵又指，使用华为手机玩游戏不会发热。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/s_b36b8135cedb443aaa-558x580.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/s_b36b8135cedb443aaa-558x580.jpg 558w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/s_b36b8135cedb443aaa.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 558px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1017/1017804.htm">快科技</a></p><p>不过就在中国媒体报道这单消息时，有心水清网民留意到手机内有些晶片仍然由台积电代工。</p><figure id="attachment_1279610" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1279610" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120633217-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1279610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120633217-694x367.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="367" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120633217-694x367.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120633217-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1279610" class="wp-caption-text">▲图片来源：快科技</figcaption></figure><p>以软件查询可见 Mate 70 晶片采用的晶片与 Pura 70 系列一样，均是 2024 年中改款麒麟 9010，至于 Mate 70 Pro、Pro+、RS 则是全新发布的麒麟 9020。麒麟 9020 与上一代 9010、9000S 一样采用 8 核 12 线程，软件识别则是 12 核心。</p><p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5-455x580.avif 455w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5.avif 600w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 455px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278153 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5-455x580.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 455px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5-455x580.jpg 455w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/fa5f990a28af456e96e5.jpg 600w" alt="" width="455" height="580" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1016/1016305.htm">快科技</a></p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>晶片</strong></td><td><strong>规格</strong></td><td><strong>GPU</strong></td><td><strong>频率</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Kirin 9020</td><td>2×2.50 GHz+6×2.15 GHz+4×1.6GHz</td><td>马良 920</td><td>840MHz</td></tr><tr><td>Kirin 9010</td><td>2×2.30 GHz+6×2.18 GHz+4×1.55GHz</td><td>马良 910</td><td>750MHz</td></tr><tr><td>Kirin 9000S</td><td>2×2.62 GHz+6×2.15 GHz+4×1.53 GHz</td><td>马良 910</td><td>750MHz</td></tr></tbody></table><p>据 Geekbench 数据显示，Kirin 9020 单核跑分表现与 2019 年推出的 iPhone 11 Pro 采用的 A13 晶片相若，但如若与 2020 年推出的 iPhone 12 Pro 采用的 A14 晶片相比，表现就稍为逊色。</p><p><picture><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278177 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449-475x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 475px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449-475x580.png 475w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155449.png 737w" alt="" width="475" height="580" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Kirin 9020 跑分结果，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a></p><p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053-469x580.avif 469w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053.avif 727w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278174 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053-469x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053-469x580.png 469w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155053.png 727w" alt="" width="469" height="580" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple A13 跑分结果，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a></p><p><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358-466x580.avif 466w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358.avif 723w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1278175 sp-no-webp" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358-466x580.png" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358-466x580.png 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241129155358.png 723w" alt="" width="466" height="580" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Apple A14 跑分结果，图片来源：<a href="https://browser.geekbench.com/v6/cpu/9128142">Geekbench</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/1017/1017804.htm">快科技</a>、Geekbench</p><p>====== 加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事 ========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
