        <item>
            <title>英国批准 Vodafone 与 3UK 合并，将成为当地最大流动电讯商网络</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/06/uk-regulator-approves-merger-of-vodafone-and-three/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=uk-regulator-approves-merger-of-vodafone-and-three</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/06/uk-regulator-approves-merger-of-vodafone-and-three/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 02:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
